-----------------------------------------
wildcards-
*-> to remove the file after that eg: touch file1,2.3 file*
{}-> add the file eg: touch file{1..20} -> this will create 
20 files
? ->  find the string eg ls ?il*
rm fi* -> it will remove the file satrt with fi
rm *le* -> start rom le 
